sp!) you don't finish a bottle of wine at the restaurant, they can "re-cork" it so it can be legally taken home to enjoy later.  Nice if you don't want to purchase by the glass.  2) Get there early - the cozy booths in the bar area go fast!  Actually, wait...  Don't get there early.  Otherwise, I won't get a good seat.  :)

